---
title: Double Striploin Steaks and Easy Scalloped Potatoes with Herby Mushrooms and Brussels Sprouts
description: Tender top sirloin steak and creamy, dreamy scalloped potatoes are guaranteed to make dinner extra special! We've simplified the potatoes by cutting them into rounds and pre-boiling them in sauce—no mandolines or long baking times tonight!
